snippet.title: Good Company - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Good Company finally releases and adds Multiplayer to the game besides many other improvements and content additions.

Good Company is available on:
EGS (demo available):  https://www.epicgames.com/store/p/good-company
Steam (demo available): https://store.steampowered.com/app/911430/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/good_company

More information at: https://goodcompanygame.com

Join the community!
Discord: https://discord.gg/goodcompany
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/GoodCompany/
